Get USPORTS basketball schedule

Source: R/basketball_schedule.R
basketball_schedule.Rd

Get USPORTS basketball schedule

Usage

basketball_schedule(gender)

Arguments

gender

Gender of athletes "m" or "w"

Value

A data frame.

Examples

basketball_schedule("m")
